high_descs: walk to the black kitchen table
grab a fork off of the black table
walk over to the microwave
place the fork inside a cup on the right side of the microwave
pick up the cup next to the microwave
bring the cup with the fork over black circle table
place the cup down on the black table
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a fork in it down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Look down slightly, turn to the left, walk to the stove, turn left, walk to the table, turn right, walk to the refrigerator, turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, walk closer to the table.
Pick up the fork next to the potato.
Turn around, walk towards the safe, turn right, walk towards the edge of the counter, turn right, cross half of the room, turn left, walk to the other side of the room to the white counter.
Place the fork in the white coffee cup on the counter.
Pick up the white coffee cup with the fork in it.
Turn left, walk to the coffee pot, turn left, walk to the end of the counter, turn right, take a step towards the refrigerator, turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, step closer to the table.
Place the coffee cup on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup with a fork in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room to the stove, then hang a left and walk over to the part of the round black table where the knife, fork, and potato are.
Pick up the metal knife next to the potato.
Turn around, take a step forward, then turn right and walk across the room to the kitchen counter where the microwave is.
Place the metal fork handle down into the white mug to the right of the microwave.
Pick up the white mug with a metal fork in it.
Turn left and walk towards the dishwasher, then hang a left and walk back over to the part of the black round table where you picked up the fork.
Place the white mug with the fork in it down on the table to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Place a white mug with a fork in it on the round black kitchen table.
